      "description": "The VanEck MSCI EAFE Analyst Sentiment ETF (VEFA) is an exchange-traded fund that is based on the MSCI EAFE Analyst Sentiment Select index. The fund tracks an index of large- and mid-cap stocks, from developed markets outside North America, that are identified to have positive analyst sentiment signals based on five revision categories namely EPS, sales, cash flow, price targets, and analyst recommendations. VEFA was launched on Apr 1, 2026 and is issued by VanEck.",
